&lt;li&gt;Develop positive relationships with local industry, government, health care providers, and key referrents to champion Northpoint’s mission in the community&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and develop employees. Create a culture that motivates employees and increases retention. Direct, coordinate, and supervise the delivery of patient care through direct and indirect supervision, evaluations, performance feedback and internal quality audits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure ongoing programmatic excellence&lt;/li&gt;
